07:31:45.720 --> 07:31:53.220
Hi, this is Tooey Sutherland.

07:31:53.279 --> 07:31:56.340
A Nightwing Guide to the Dragons of

07:31:56.340 --> 07:31:56.939
Pyrea.

07:31:57.060 --> 07:31:59.220
Sand wings.

07:31:59.279 --> 07:32:00.779
Description.

07:32:00.840 --> 07:32:03.479
Pale gold or white scales, the color of

07:32:03.479 --> 07:32:07.439
desert sand, Poisonous barbed tail, Forked

07:32:07.439 --> 07:32:08.099
black tongues.

07:32:08.220 --> 07:32:12.180
Abilities can survive a long time without

07:32:12.180 --> 07:32:12.540
water.

07:32:12.599 --> 07:32:14.939
Poison enemies with the tips of their

07:32:14.939 --> 07:32:16.020
tails like scorpions.

07:32:16.080 --> 07:32:18.540
Bury themselves for camouflage in the

07:32:18.540 --> 07:32:19.139
desert sand.

07:32:19.200 --> 07:32:20.580
Breathe fire.

07:32:20.639 --> 07:32:22.680
Queen.

07:32:22.740 --> 07:32:25.619
Since the death of Queen Oasis, the tribe

07:32:25.619 --> 07:32:27.360
is split between 3 rivals for the

07:32:27.360 --> 07:32:27.900
throne.

07:32:27.900 --> 07:32:30.779
Sisters burn, blister, and blaze.

07:32:30.900 --> 07:32:33.240
Alliances.

07:32:33.360 --> 07:32:36.540
Byrne fights alongside Skywings and

07:32:36.540 --> 07:32:37.080
Mudwings.

07:32:37.139 --> 07:32:40.560
Blister is allied with the sea wings, and

07:32:40.560 --> 07:32:42.900
Blaze has the support of most sand wings

07:32:42.900 --> 07:32:44.400
as well as an alliance with the ice

07:32:44.400 --> 07:32:44.759
wings.

07:32:44.819 --> 07:32:47.340
Mudwings.

07:32:47.400 --> 07:32:51.540
Description, thick armored brown scales

07:32:51.540 --> 07:32:52.799
sometimes with amber and gold

07:32:52.799 --> 07:32:53.580
underscales.

07:32:53.639 --> 07:32:56.459
Large flat heads with nostrils on top of

07:32:56.459 --> 07:32:56.880
the snout.

07:32:57.000 --> 07:33:00.659
Abilities, can breathe fire if warm

07:33:00.659 --> 07:33:00.959
enough.

07:33:01.020 --> 07:33:04.259
Hold their breath for up to an hour, blend

07:33:04.259 --> 07:33:06.599
into large mud puddles, usually very

07:33:06.599 --> 07:33:06.959
strong.

07:33:06.959 --> 07:33:10.139
Queen, Queen Moorhen.

07:33:10.200 --> 07:33:14.099
Alliances, currently allied with burn and

07:33:14.099 --> 07:33:15.419
the sky wings in the Great War.

07:33:15.479 --> 07:33:18.180
Sky Wings.

07:33:18.299 --> 07:33:21.900
Description, red gold or orange scales

07:33:21.900 --> 07:33:22.919
enormous wings.

07:33:23.040 --> 07:33:27.119
Abilities, powerful fighters and flyers

07:33:27.119 --> 07:33:28.259
can breathe fire.

07:33:28.319 --> 07:33:31.259
Queen, Queen Scarlet.

07:33:31.380 --> 07:33:35.279
Alliances, currently allied with burn and

07:33:35.279 --> 07:33:36.479
the mud wings in the Great War.

07:33:36.540 --> 07:33:39.299
C Wings.

07:33:39.360 --> 07:33:43.020
Description, blue or green or aquamarine

07:33:43.020 --> 07:33:46.380
scales, webs between their claws, gills

07:33:46.380 --> 07:33:48.720
on their necks, glow in the dark stripes

07:33:48.720 --> 07:33:50.520
on their tails, snouts, underbellies.

07:33:50.580 --> 07:33:54.900
Abilities, can breathe underwater, see in

07:33:54.900 --> 07:33:57.240
the dark, create huge waves with one

07:33:57.240 --> 07:33:58.560
splash of their powerful tails.

07:33:58.619 --> 07:34:00.360
Excellent swimmers.

07:34:00.419 --> 07:34:03.540
Queen, Queen Coral.

07:34:03.599 --> 07:34:07.560
Alliances, currently allied with blister

07:34:07.560 --> 07:34:08.340
in the Great War.

07:34:08.400 --> 07:34:10.979
Ice Wings.

07:34:11.040 --> 07:34:12.419
Description.

07:34:12.540 --> 07:34:14.880
Silvery scales like the moon, or pale

07:34:14.880 --> 07:34:15.840
blue like ice.

07:34:15.900 --> 07:34:19.799
Ridged claws to grip the ice, forked blue

07:34:19.799 --> 07:34:22.319
tongues, tails narrow to a whip thin

07:34:22.319 --> 07:34:22.500
end.

07:34:22.619 --> 07:34:26.520
Abilities can withstand subzero

07:34:26.520 --> 07:34:27.900
temperatures and bright light.

07:34:28.020 --> 07:34:30.060
Exhale a deadly, freezing breath.

07:34:30.119 --> 07:34:33.299
Queen, Queen Glacier.

07:34:33.419 --> 07:34:35.340
Alliances.

07:34:35.340 --> 07:34:37.860
Currently allied with Blaze and most of

07:34:37.860 --> 07:34:39.479
the sandwings in the Great War.

07:34:39.540 --> 07:34:41.819
Rain wings.

07:34:41.880 --> 07:34:45.119
Description, scales constantly shift

07:34:45.119 --> 07:34:47.099
